current {rbrr_chosen_vmimage_sha} value (if set)
.. {rbbc_show}
latest upstream SHA: `«UPSTREAM_SHA»`
.. {rbbc_show}
required action:
... If {rbrr_chosen_vmimage_sha} not set: "Please set RBRR_CHOSEN_VMIMAGE_SHA to «UPSTREAM_SHA»"
